import React from 'react'
import SectionHeader from './SectionHeader'
import CaseStudyArchived from './CaseStudyArchived'

export default function Contact() {
  return (
    <footer className="section-container">
        <SectionHeader description="05 / 05 | CONTACT" title="Get in Touch" />
        <CaseStudyArchived
            projectName = "Email"
            projectDescription = "My preferred method of communication"
            link = "mailto:hello@goksudayan.com"
        />
        <CaseStudyArchived
            projectName = "LinkedIn"
            projectDescription = "Let's connect on the world's largest network for professionals"
            link = "https://www.linkedin.com/in/goksudayan"
        />
        <CaseStudyArchived
            projectName = "Medium"
            projectDescription = "My occasional mind dumps reside here"
            link = "https://goksudayan.medium.com"
        />
        <CaseStudyArchived
            projectName = "Calendly"
            projectDescription= "In case you need to set up a meeting ASAP"
            link = "https://calendly.com/goksudayan/meeting-with-goksu-dayan"
        />
        <CaseStudyArchived
            projectName = "Github"
            projectDescription = "Some of my code reside here"
            link = "https://github.com/goksudayan"
        />
    </footer>

  )
}
